{
  "stem": "24111.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And thousands of new immigrants came to Palestine between '49 and '51, and that was only the first wave of immigrants.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Those immigrants were not-- were not-- were not Zionists.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were not the caliber we had when I came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Those were people from Algeria, from Morocco, displaced persons from Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The saying was [NON-ENGLISH]-- we have no other choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That is the reason they came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that was the time when I say, OK, now I want to look for a better life and a different life-- let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I decided to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Something else pushed a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "When I was in Switzerland in 1945, before knowing that I ever will get a certificate to come to the-- to Palestine legally, I put in for the Austrian quota to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "At that time, the Austrian quota took five years waiting till your number came up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "In 1951, my number came up, and I could get legal entry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I could get an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So I took the opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the notification came from the United States, actually.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
